location: This project involved the rehabilitation and expansion of the 17.4 section of the Accra-Kumasi Trunk Road between Ofankor and Nsawam. It also included the construction of a 20 meter fly-over bridge over the rail line near Ofankor, which has a 13 ton capacity.
